rComments: The prof is outright terrible, however it doesn't matter since the course itself is extremely easy. Don't ask him questions in class, he won't answer it and instead make fun of you. Attending class is useless and as long as you do the biweekly homework, it's an easy A.

Beware: there are tons of mistakes in his slides. He's unprofessional and rude, so don't ask questions during class. Ever. Ask him after class individually.
